{
  "script_id": "solid-of-revolution",
  "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural",
  "voice_key": "yunxi",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "solid-of-revolution",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/solid-of-revolution/yunxi/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.22,
      "size": 35568,
      "text": "取一条曲线 y 等于 f(x)，让它绕着 x 轴转一整圈。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "solid-of-revolution",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/solid-of-revolution/yunxi/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.93,
      "size": 30816,
      "text": "曲线扫过的空间，就围出了一个立体，我们叫它旋转体。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "solid-of-revolution",
      "section_id": "disk",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "disk-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/solid-of-revolution/yunxi/disk-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.49,
      "size": 23904,
      "text": "把立体沿 x 方向切成许多薄薄的圆盘。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "solid-of-revolution",
      "section_id": "disk",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "disk-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/solid-of-revolution/yunxi/disk-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.83,
      "size": 45360,
      "text": "每个圆盘的半径正好是 f(x)，面积就是 π 乘 f(x) 的平方。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "solid-of-revolution",
      "section_id": "disk",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "disk-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/solid-of-revolution/yunxi/disk-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.53,
      "size": 24480,
      "text": "再乘上薄薄的厚度，就是一片圆盘的体积。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "solid-of-revolution",
      "section_id": "integral",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "integral-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/solid-of-revolution/yunxi/integral-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.49,
      "size": 39888,
      "text": "于是体积等于从 a 到 b，对 π f(x) 平方求定积分。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "solid-of-revolution",
      "section_id": "integral",
      "line_id": "int-3",
      "filename": "integral-int-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/solid-of-revolution/yunxi/integral-int-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.93,
      "size": 30816,
      "text": "计算机用辛普森法做数值积分，能精确地逼近这个值。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "solid-of-revolution",
      "section_id": "shell",
      "line_id": "shl-1",
      "filename": "shell-shl-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/solid-of-revolution/yunxi/shell-shl-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.17,
      "size": 34704,
      "text": "换个视角，我们也能沿 y 方向，把立体套成一层层薄圆筒。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "solid-of-revolution",
      "section_id": "shell",
      "line_id": "shl-2",
      "filename": "shell-shl-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/solid-of-revolution/yunxi/shell-shl-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32400,
      "text": "每层圆筒的体积是 2π 乘半径 y，再乘它的高与厚度。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "solid-of-revolution",
      "section_id": "shell",
      "line_id": "shl-3",
      "filename": "shell-shl-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/solid-of-revolution/yunxi/shell-shl-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.19,
      "size": 34992,
      "text": "这就是壳层法，它和圆盘法算的是同一个立体，结果必然相等。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "solid-of-revolution",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "ita-1",
      "filename": "interaction-ita-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/solid-of-revolution/yunxi/interaction-ita-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.12,
      "size": 33984,
      "text": "换一条曲线，或者拖动积分区间，看看体积如何随之改变。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "solid-of-revolution",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "ita-2",
      "filename": "interaction-ita-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/solid-of-revolution/yunxi/interaction-ita-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.0,
      "size": 31968,
      "text": "注意屏幕上圆盘法与壳层法给出的数字，始终紧紧咬合。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "solid-of-revolution",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/solid-of-revolution/yunxi/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.88,
      "size": 30096,
      "text": "旋转体的体积，可以切成圆盘,也可以套成壳层。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "solid-of-revolution",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/solid-of-revolution/yunxi/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.2,
      "size": 35136,
      "text": "两条思路都用积分把无数薄片累加成整体，答案完全一致。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "solid-of-revolution",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/solid-of-revolution/yunxi/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.26,
      "size": 36144,
      "text": "一样的立体，两种视角，这就是微积分的美妙，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
